  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104560/extras/e34e323b381340e9c95780e808113a2e.avif?t=1667034449\" width=616 height=208 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dream, time, and memories </h2><strong>Mom and dad are disappeared!</strong> In the middle of night, while a girl woke up and wandering around home, she fell on the rusty garbage dump. Can Sowon go back to her world out from this strange world?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104560/extras/7069759b36f4a91f896d772e047f073f.poster.avif?t=1667034449\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104560/extras/7069759b36f4a91f896d772e047f073f.webm?t=1667034449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104560/extras/7069759b36f4a91f896d772e047f073f.mp4?t=1667034449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ㅡGot an invitation from the ugliest doll!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Can Sowon wake up if she would tumble and fall?<br></li><li>In the toy world, beauty and fear coexist and all living things are toys. There also might be a toy you want.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104560/extras/3383cd41f8ede63b93f725b015141f1c.poster.avif?t=1667034449\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104560/extras/3383cd41f8ede63b93f725b015141f1c.webm?t=1667034449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104560/extras/3383cd41f8ede63b93f725b015141f1c.mp4?t=1667034449\" 